1 cups flour
1 tbsp flour
1/2 tsp baking soda
1/2 tsp salt (omit if butter is salted)
1/2 cup butter
1/4 cup white sugar
1/2 cup brown sugar
1 tsp vanilla
1 egg
1 cups chocolate chips

Choice:
1/2 cup nuts
1 tbsp flour

Optional:
1 1/2 tsp instant coffee
Citrus zest

bake 375F nonconvection 10min, cool 5min
Or bake 300F nonconvection 20min, cool 5min (crispier)
